metadata.name: Postpartum
metadata.description:
This artwork expresses a feeling of both joy and horror a new mother (not all) has to go through post-pregnancy. Postpartum depression is not talked about much but is crippling for those who go through it. 

The mother's expressions represent uncertainty, doubt, and scared because of her struggles. Still, she is surrounded by beautiful vibrant colors representing the joy and liveliness brought into her world by the newborn child.


Artworks in this collections are a blend of experimentation with Human prompts x AI.

Created using DALL-E by OpenAI.
